data.name: ReadDisbSuppressionStatusHistory1
data.value: select top(1) T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.DSS_GENERATED_ID, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.LAST_UPDATED_BY, T1.LAST_UPDATED_TMST, T1.TYPE, T1.REASON_TEXT, T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION T4 join CKT_DISB_SUPPR_STS T1 on (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = @cpaType) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (T1.TYPE = 'O') and (T4.LEGAL_ACTION_ID = T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER) and (T4.STANDARD_NO = @standardNo)

data.name: ReadDisbSuppressionStatusHistory2
data.value: select top(1) T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.DSS_GENERATED_ID, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.LAST_UPDATED_BY, T1.LAST_UPDATED_TMST, T1.TYPE, T1.REASON_TEXT, T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION T4 join CKT_DISB_SUPPR_STS T1 on (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = @cpaType) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (T1.TYPE = 'O') and (T4.LEGAL_ACTION_ID = T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER) and (T4.STANDARD_NO = @standardNo)

data.name: ReadDisbSuppressionStatusHistory3
data.value: select top(1) CPA_TYPE, CSP_NUMBER, DSS_GENERATED_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, TYPE, REASON_TEXT, LGA_IDENTIFIER from CKT_DISB_SUPPR_STS where (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (CPA_TYPE = @cpaType) and (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (TYPE = 'P')

data.name: ReadDisbSuppressionStatusHistory4
data.value: select top(1) CPA_TYPE, CSP_NUMBER, DSS_GENERATED_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, TYPE, REASON_TEXT, LGA_IDENTIFIER from CKT_DISB_SUPPR_STS where (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (CPA_TYPE = @cpaType) and (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (TYPE = 'P')

data.name: ReadDisbSuppressionStatusHistory5
data.value: select distinct top(1) T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.DSS_GENERATED_ID, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.LAST_UPDATED_BY, T1.LAST_UPDATED_TMST, T1.TYPE, T1.REASON_TEXT, T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION T4 join CKT_DISB_SUPPR_STS T1 on (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE > @effectiveDate) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE > @effectiveDate) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = @cpaType) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (T1.TYPE = 'O') and (T4.LEGAL_ACTION_ID = T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER) and (T4.STANDARD_NO = @standardNo) order by T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE

data.name: ReadDisbSuppressionStatusHistory6
data.value: select top(1) CPA_TYPE, CSP_NUMBER, DSS_GENERATED_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, TYPE, REASON_TEXT, LGA_IDENTIFIER from CKT_DISB_SUPPR_STS where (EFFECTIVE_DATE > @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE > @effectiveDate) and (CPA_TYPE = @cpaType) and (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (TYPE = 'P') order by EFFECTIVE_DATE

data.name: ReadLegalAction
data.value: select top(1) LEGAL_ACTION_ID, STANDARD_NO from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION where STANDARD_NO = @standardNo
